# notes

## The demo

## lab one 

build a contianer that pushes pictures to minio

## lab two 

build a container that randomly displays the images from part one

### Container will need

* ~AWS cli + AWS API Key and Secret~ Minio lib
* Webpage for displaying images
* Script to push pictures to minio

Commands:
```
$ aws s3 cp "IMAGEPATH" s3://kw2018-container-pod/images
$ aws s3 cp s3://kw2018-container-pod/images ./
```

Running the docker container:
```
$ docker run -it --rm --name app-test1 -p 5000:5000 -e AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID="" -e AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY="" test:latest kw2018-container-pod /images/cat.png png

$ docker run -it --rm --name app-test1 -p 8000:8000 -e AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID="" -e AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY="" test-2:latest /usr/src/app/simple-uploader.py
```
